        <updateDate>2008-04-08T16:49:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Gold Star Parents Annuity Act of 2007 - Directs the Secretary of Defense to pay a special pension to each person who has received a Gold Star lapel button as a parent of a member of the Armed Forces who died while serving.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
