      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 38, United States Code, to provide for the payment of a monthly stipend to the surviving parents (known as "Gold Star parents") of members of the Armed Forces who die during a period of war.</title>
      </item>
